1. *Grudi* su mi se odmarale u toplini sunca. (My breasts were resting in the warmth of the sun.) 
2. *Grudima* je hladnije nego područjima tijela. (The breasts are cooler than other parts of the body.)
3. *Grudi* su bile vruće od napora. (The breasts were hot from the effort.)
4. Stiskao je *grudi* očajno. (He grasped her breasts desperately.)
5. Ona je imala čvrste, obline *grudi*. (She had firm, shapely breasts.)